svndeploy is a tool for pushing changes out to a production server

Contents of this distribution:

    Makefile        full installation instructions

    README          this file

    svndeploy.1     manual page

    svndeploy.py    script itself


To install:

    % cd ~
    % svn export http://www.zetadev.com/svn/public/svndeploy/trunk svndeploy
    % cd svndeploy
    % make install


To uninstall:

    % cd ~/svndeploy
    % make uninstall
